svg.title: Clouds of the genera Altocumulus, Altostratus and Nimbostratus: Altocumulus translucidus at a single level
svg.desc: WMO international weather symbol: Clouds of the genera Altocumulus, Altostratus and Nimbostratus: Altocumulus, the greater part of which is semi-transparent; the various elements of the cloud change only slowly and are all at a single level
